    <briefdescription>
<para>A class for generating noise functions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="classhmap_1_1NoiseFunction" kindref="compound">NoiseFunction</ref></computeroutput> class provides an interface for generating noise-based functions. It inherits from the <computeroutput><ref refid="classhmap_1_1Function" kindref="compound">Function</ref></computeroutput> class and adds parameters for frequency scaling (<computeroutput>kw</computeroutput>) and a random seed (<computeroutput>seed</computeroutput>) to customize the noise generation. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
